movie.title: Mars Attacks!
movie.plot: 'We come in peace' is not what those green men from Mars mean when they invade our planet, armed with irresistible weapons and a cruel sense of humor.  This star studded cast must play victim to the alienâ€™s fun and games in this comedy homage to science fiction films of the '50s and '60s.
